Sam Ash (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sam_Ash_(actor) 0 Samuel Howard Ash (August 28, 1884 – October 20, 1951), usually credited as Sam Ash, was an American vaudeville performer, singer, and movie actor who appeared in minor roles in over 200 films, including It's a Wonderful Life.
